&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, Times; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Цвет столешницы:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
